resorts.description: This resort offers award winning children's programs and one of the best skiing and snowboarding experiences in the East.

alertMessages.alertTitle: WM Owner Club Pass Check In Age Alert

helpfulHints: A resort fee ranging from $47-57 is required at check-in
Ride the on-site shuttle to enjoy the resort's amenities. It's available at select times during the winter and summer.
Skiers can ride the shuttle to the upper mountain, available at select times during the winter. Pick-up is near the welcome sign in the Village.
Suite types and size vary by building and are based on availability.

The physical terrain at Smugglers' Notch is not readily accessible; the roads and walkways are unpaved and most buildings are on the slope side or hillside with no elevators and may require multiple flights of stairs.
resorts.name: Club Wyndham Smugglers' Notch Vermont
